caption: b'Thank you to all our Veterans and their families #wearealpa'

b'The United pilot-approved Pandemic Recovery Agreement stops United pilot furloughs. Now it\xe2\x80\x99s time for Congress to extend a lifeline to all airline employees. #essentialworkers #wearealpa'

b'United pilots voted to approve the Pandemic Recovery Letter of Agreement with United Airlines. The agreement will keep all 13,000 United pilots employed and cancels the 2850 previously announced furloughs. #pilotsprotectingpilots'
b'The Pandemic Recovery Letter of Agreement has been approved by United pilots. #pilotsprotectingpilots #wearealpa'
b'United pilots Capt. Brian Florence and Capt. Bob Ward honor the memory of\xc2\xa0United\xc2\xa0First Officer LeRoy Homer at the Flight 93 National Memorial.'
b'Today, we solemnly mark 19 years since the September 11 terrorist attacks. On behalf of all United pilots, our hearts go out to those who were lost and their loved ones. We will never forget.'

b'Labor unions, including ALPA, help break down barriers for women and minorities. Since 1978, when these three pioneers were the first women to be hired at United, women aviators have helped build United Airlines and ALPA into what they are today.'

b'For nearly a century, United pilots have been proudly serving customers, flying, cargo, and even getting the mail where it needed to go. On this #NationalAviationDay, the United MEC wants to thank all our pilots for doing what they love every day and taking to the skies.'
